videos.description: Georgia's Jacob Eason passes to Isaiah McKenzie for 77-yard catch, setting up the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Georgia sets tempo with 77 yard catch

videos.description: Georgia's Sony Michel runs for a 4-yard touchdown to give the Bulldogs the lead.
videos.headline: Georgia gets on the board with rushing TD

videos.description: Georgia's Jacob Eason fumbles off a big hit from Tipa Galeai, Mat Boesen recovers. TCU gets the ball in the red zone.
videos.headline: TCU forces fumble off big hit on Eason

videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill keeps it for the 10-yard run for a touchdown.
videos.headline: TCU's Hill runs it into the end zone

videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill passes to John Diarse for the 10-yard catch, giving the Horned Frogs another touchdown.
videos.headline: Hill finds Diarse for 10-yard score

videos.description: TCU QB Kenny Hill scampers 45 yards, setting up the Horned Frogs in the red zone.
videos.headline: Hill takes it himself for the 45-yard run

videos.description: Georgia's Jacob Eason passes to Sony Michel, who sheds tacklers and rolls in the end zone for the 33-yard score.
videos.headline: Georgia's Michel rolls into the end zone for the TD

videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill buys time, but Lorenzo Carter forces the fumble and Trenton Thompson recovers it for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Georgia strips Hill and recovers the fumble

videos.description: TCU head coach Gary Patterson takes the blame for letting Georgia gets big plays on offense in the first half.
videos.headline: TCU coach Gary Patterson takes blame for Georgia's big plays

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart talks about the performance of Bulldogs' QB Jacob Eason and TCU QB Kenny Hill in the first half.
videos.headline: Georgia coach Kirby Smart on QB play

videos.description: Georgia's Lorenzo Carter forces his second fumble, Dominick Sanders recovers it for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Georgia forces fumble on TCU's opening drive in 2nd half

videos.description: Georgia fakes the Field Goal, and Brice Ramsey runs it 11-yards for the first down to extend the Bulldogs drive.
videos.headline: Georgia fakes the FG to extend drive

videos.description: Georgia's Jacob Eason throws it to Javon Wims for the 4-yard touchdown and the lead for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Wims scores to give Georgia the lead

videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill throws it to John Diarse who makes the spectacular catch in the end zone for the 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Diarse makes the unbelievable catch in the end zone

videos.description: Georgia's Nick Chubb surges upfield for the 48-yard gain, placing the Bulldogs in the red zone.
videos.headline: Chubb rumbles for 48 yards

videos.description: Georgia's Rodrigo Blankenship hits the 30-yard field goal to help the Bulldogs take advantage of the early missed PAT from TCU.
videos.headline: UGA's FG give Bulldogs the late lead

videos.description: TCU's Brandon Hatfield misses the 47-yard field goal, which would have given the Horned Frogs the late lead.
videos.headline: TCU misses potential go-ahead FG

videos.description: Georgia's Nick Chubb powers his way into the end zone for the 13-yard touchdown, padding the Bulldogs' lead 31-23.
videos.headline: Chubb keeps feet moving to get TD

videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill can't connect with Taj Williams on 4th down, Horned Frogs turn the ball over on downs with a minute remaining in the Liberty Bowl.
videos.headline: TCU can't convert on 4th down

videos.description: Georgia's Nick Chubb runs it for 27-yards to put a cap on the Liberty Bowl against TCU.
videos.headline: Nick Chubb seals win with a 27-yard run

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart talks about the significance of winning his first bowl game as a head coach.
videos.headline: Georgia coach Kirby Smart talks on first bowl victory

videos.description: Georgia lifts the Liberty Bowl trophy and head coach Kirby Smart talks about the performance of the team against TCU.
videos.headline: Georgia lifts the Liberty Bowl Trophy

videos.description: Georgia RB Sony Michel shares why he decided to return for another year of Bulldog football.
videos.headline: Michel:' It's a bond that can never be broken'

videos.description: Liberty Bowl MVP and Georgia DT Trenton Thompson speaks on the strength and power of the Bulldogs' defense.
videos.headline: Liberty Bowl MVP Trenton Thompson talks defensive strength

videos.description: Breaking down Georgia's victory over TCU in the Liberty Bowl.
videos.headline: Breaking down Georgia's Liberty Bowl victory
